  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> and <strong>1 MP</strong> to Curse a creature within 5 Spaces for 1 minute.</p><p>The target must make a <strong>Repeated Physical Save</strong> against your <strong>Save DC</strong>.</p><p><strong>Failure:</strong> It contracts 1 of the following Curses of your choice:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Umbral Rot:</strong> The target’s flesh begins to decay and peel, causing it to take 1 Umbral damage at the start of each of its turns.</p></li><li><p><strong>Black Blood:</strong> The target’s blood turns black, preventing it from regaining HP. Creature’s without blood are immune to this effect.</p></li><li><p><strong>Sickening Fever:</strong> The target contracts a deadly fever, causing it to become <strong>Dazed</strong> or <strong>Impaired</strong> (your choice).</p></li></ul>",
